(7275, 'Levoxin 500mg 5 f.c. tab.', 'ليفوكسين 500 مجم 5 اقراص', '', '76', 'Levofloxacin', 'Amoun', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد حيوي', 'Antibiotic.quinolone', '500mg', 'In oral and intravenous formulations, levofloxacin is indicated in adults for the treatment of various infections caused by susceptible bacteria, including infections of the upper respiratory tract, lower respiratory tract, skin, skin structures, urinary tract, and prostate.[L11638,L11692] The oral formulation is also indicated in both adults and children 6 months of age and older for the post-exposure management of inhalational anthrax caused by _Bacillus anthracis_ and for the treatment and/or prophylaxis of plague caused by _Yersinia pestis_.[L11638]
