(16218, 'Omegafolina 30 caps.', 'اوميجافولينا 30 كبسولة', '', '60', 'Fish oil+l-methylfolate', 'Mepaco', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Multivitamin', '', 'Under FDA approval, fish oil pharmaceuticals are typically products consisting of a combination of the omega-3-fatty acids eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and are indicated primarily as an adjunct to diet to reduce triglyceride levels in adult patients with severe (>=500 mg/dL) hypertriglyceridemia [FDA Label, F36].
